Changes in the management and comorbidities of acromegaly over three decades: 
the French Acromegaly Registry.

Maione L(1)(2)(3), Brue T(4), Beckers A(5), Delemer B(6), Petrossians P(5), 
Borson-Chazot F(7)(8)(9), Chabre O(10), François P(11), Bertherat J(12), 
