When surgery is not an option: is there a clinical need for transcatheter 
tricuspid valve therapies?

Vahanian A(1), Juliard JM(2), Brochet E(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Cardiology, Hôpital Bichat, University of Paris VI, Paris, 
